name: ruscoin
desc: RusCoin is a fintech project aimed at investing assets raised through ICO in various business projects in Russia and worldwide as promoted by Russian founders with an Internal Rate of Return of more than 35%. Our primary investment target is a blocking stake in Moscow Exchange (PJSC). This asset is hugely undervalued, and our goal is to introduce blockchain companies and crypto-assets to this legitimate exchange. Buyers of RusCoin tokens become co-owners of existing and profitable businesses and/or readily obtainable assets, while the blockchain technology ensures complete transparency and traceability of all our transactions and investment projects run by RusCoin project team. The smart contract mechanism is one of the tools to ensure such transparency.

name: crypto noda
desc: Crypto Noda is the first automated hosting service for connection, activation, analytics and maintenance of masternode. The idea of the project is simple and clear - the creation of an automated hosting service that allows you to connect any masternode in a couple of clicks. And most importantly, the activation of the masternode unlimited number of coins is completely free, without premature fees. In turn, the service will work exclusively on % of the net profit of partners.

name: onetotwo
desc: OTT-token gives a full (100%) guarantee of payments to its holder, with the expected 100% payback ranges from 1 month (in the most favorable variant) and up to 8 months (in the most unfavorable variant). If the investor decides to refuse to participate in the project, he will be able to apply for the sale of tokens, for this we have developed a Funds Recovery Fund" (FRF) for 100% protection of the interests of its investors. Funds Recovery Fund is formed from the sale of tokens in the amount of 30% and from instant bets in the amount of 1%. Each investor has the right to apply for the sale of his token(s) at full cost. The token will be automatically redeemed by the Issuer with Funds Recovery Fund after 90 days from the date of application. The token is redeemed strictly at the cost of the purchase price
ticker: depending on the stage of purchase at the ICO and the received referral discount."
